    "description": "Right now we include the installation instructions for pip in the same section as the source install. This made sense when we were not building and shipping wheels but does not make sense now. In fact, one can just do \"pip install yt\" on linux, OSX, or windows and it should \"just work\" modulo permission issues.\r\n\r\nThis also makes for a clearer place to send people who want instructions on how to build yt from source.",
